# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok taiwan share prices closed #.## percent higher tuesday in active trade driven by gains in taiwan semiconductor manufacturing co. -lrb- tsmc -rrb- and the broader electronics sector , dealers said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (d / deal-01))
      :ARG1 (c / close-01
            :ARG1 (p2 / price-01
                  :ARG1 (s2 / share
                        :mod (c2 / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Taiwan"))))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / tuesday))
            :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (t2 / trade-01
                        :ARG1-of (a / activity-06)
                        :ARG1-of (d3 / drive-02
                              :ARG0 (g / gain-02
                                    :ARG0 (a2 / and
                                          :op1 (c4 / company
                                                :ARG0-of (m / manufacture-01
                                                      :ARG1 (s3 / semiconductor))
                                                :mod c2)
                                          :op2 (s4 / sector
                                                :mod (e / electronics)
                                                :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                                                      :ARG2 (b / broad-02
                                                            :ARG1 s4)
                                                      :ARG3 (m2 / more)
                                                      :ARG1 c3))))))
                  :ARG2 (h2 / high-02
                        :ARG1 t2)
                  :ARG3 m2
                  :quant (p3 / percentage-entity
                        :value 1))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the shenzhen component index on the shenzhen stock exchange closed higher friday to end at ##,###.## points , up ###.## points , or #.## percent .
# ::alignments
(c / close-01
      :ARG1 (ii / index
            :mod (c2 / component)
            :location (e / exchange-01
                  :ARG1 (s / stock)
                  :location (c3 / city
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Shenzhen"))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
            :ARG2 (h2 / high-02
                  :ARG1 c)
            :ARG3 (m / more))
      :ARG1-of (e2 / end-01
            :ARG2 (o / or
                  :op1 (p / point
                        :mod (s2 / string-entity
                              :value "##"))
                  :op2 (p2 / point
                        :mod s2)
                  :op3 (p3 / point
                        :mod s2
                        :mod (u / up))
                  :op4 (p4 / percentage
                        :mod s2))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok daron rahlves won the men 's world cup <unk> here friday , leading reigning world cup overall champion bode miller in a crowd-pleasing us one-two finish ahead of austrian hans grugger .

      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Daron"
                  :op2 "Rahlves"))
      :ARG1 (g / game
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "World"
                  :op2 "Cup")
            :mod (m / men))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :location (h / here)
      :ARG0-of (c / cause-01
            :ARG1 (l / lead-02
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Bode"
                              :op2 "Mealer")
                        :ARG0-of (r / reign-01)
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 g
                              :ARG2 (c2 / champion
                                    :mod (o / overall))))
                  :manner (f2 / finish-07
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG2 (p3 / person
                              :quant 2)
                        :manner (c3 / crowd-01)
                        :time (a / ahead
                              :op1 (p4 / person
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Hans"
                                          :op2 "Grugger")
                                    :mod (c4 / country
                                          :name (n5 / name
                                                :op1 "Australia"))))))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the leading metalworkers union at airbus sas wednesday appealed to the french government to pressure its european allies to save the troubled a###m military transport program and protect thousands of jobs .

      :ARG0 (u / union
            :consist-of (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (w / work-01
                        :ARG1 (m / metal)))
            :ARG0-of (l / lead-02)
            :location (c / company
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Airbus")))
      :ARG1 (g / government-organization
            :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01
                  :ARG1 (c2 / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "France"))))
      :ARG2 (p2 / pressure-01
            :ARG0 g
            :ARG1 (c3 / country
                  :ARG1-of (a2 / ally-01
                        :ARG2 c2)
                  :mod (c4 / continent
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Europe")))
            :ARG2 (a3 / and
                  :op1 (s / save-02
                        :ARG0 c3
                        :ARG1 (p3 / program
                              :topic (t / transport-01
                                    :mod (m2 / military))
                              :ARG1-of (t2 / trouble-01)
                              :mod (m3 / monetary-quantity
                                    :quant 1500000000
                                    :unit (p4 / pound))))
                  :op2 (p5 / protect-01
                        :ARG0 c3
                        :ARG1 (j / job
                              :quant (m4 / multiple
                                    :op1 1000)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (w2 / wednesday)))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok pakistan temporarily closed the major supply route to u.s. and nato forces in afghanistan on monday after suspected insurgents firing rockets killed a soldier at a pakistani military camp -- the latest attack to highlight the vulnerability of the legendary khyber pass .
# ::alignments
(c / close-01
      :ARG0 (c2 / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Afghanistan"))
      :ARG1 (r / route
            :path-of (s / supply-01)
            :ARG1-of (m / major-02)
            :destination (a / and
                  :op1 (f / force
                        :mod (m2 / military))
                  :op2 (f2 / force
                        :mod (m3 / military))))
      :duration (t / temporary)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m4 / monday))
      :time (a2 / after
            :op1 (k / kill-01
                  :ARG0 (ii / insurgent
                        :ARG2-of (s2 / suspect-01)
                        :ARG0-of (f3 / fire-01
                              :ARG1 (r2 / rocket)))
                  :ARG1 (s3 / soldier)
                  :location (c3 / camp
                        :mod (m5 / military)
                        :mod (c4 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Pakistan"))))
            :ARG1-of (a3 / attack-01
                  :mod (l / last)
                  :ARG0-of (h / highlight-01
                        :ARG1 (v / vulnerable-01
                              :ARG1 (p / pass
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Khyber"
                                          :op2 "Pass")
                                    :mod (l2 / legendary)))))))

                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "State"
                              :op2 "Department")

                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "U.S.")))
                  :ARG2 (d / diplomat)))
      :ARG1 (p2 / person
            :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c2 / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "South"
                              :op2 "Korea"))
                  :ARG2 (c3 / counterpart)))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday))
      :time (d3 / discuss-01
            :ARG0 (a / and
                  :op1 (p3 / person
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Washington"))
                  :op2 (p4 / person
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Seoul")))
            :ARG1 (t2 / thing
                  :manner-of (e / ensure-01
                        :ARG0 a
                        :ARG1 (k / keep-02
                              :ARG0 (c4 / country
                                    :name (n6 / name
                                          :op1 "North"
                                          :op2 "Korea"))
                              :ARG1 (p5 / pledge-01
                                    :ARG0 c4

                                          :ARG0 c4

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok indian shares plunged #.## percent on monday , as investors were spooked by a government budget that warned efforts to spur growth would result in a widening fiscal deficit , dealers said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (d / deal-01))
      :ARG1 (p2 / plunge-01
            :ARG1 (s2 / share
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "India")))
            :ARG2 (p3 / percentage-entity
                  :value ".##")
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (m / monday))
            :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (s3 / spook-01
                        :ARG0 (b / budget-01
                              :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                                    :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01))
                              :ARG0-of (w / warn-01
                                    :ARG1 (r / result-01
                                          :ARG1 (e / effort-01
                                                :ARG1 (s4 / spur-01
                                                      :ARG1 (g3 / grow-01)))
                                          :ARG2 (d3 / deficit
                                                :mod (f / finance)
                                                :ARG1-of (w2 / widen-01))))
                              :ARG1 (p4 / person
                                    :ARG0-of (ii / invest-01)))))))

                                    :unit (d2 / dollar))))))

# ::alignments
(a / appear-01
      :ARG1 (l / lady
            :quant 2
            :ARG1-of (f / familiarize-01
                  :polarity -))
      :location (f2 / festival
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Caramoor"
                  :op2 "International"
                  :op3 "Music"
                  :op4 "Festival")
            :mod (m / music)
            :mod (ii / international)
            :ARG1-of (a2 / anticipate-01
                  :ARG1-of (l2 / long-03))
            :mod (o / other)
            :ARG1-of (s / surprise-01
                  :time (m2 / minute
                        :mod (l3 / last)))))

# ::alignments

      :ARG0 (h / he)
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (t / thing
                  :ARG0-of (m / make-02
                        :ARG1 (t2 / tick-03
                              :ARG0 (p / person
                                    :ARG0-of (p2 / play-01)
                                    :mod (y / young)))))
            :op2 t
            :manner-of (m2 / motivate-01
                  :ARG1 p)))

# ::alignments

            :poss (p / person
                  :name (n / name

                        :ARG1 (c / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "United"
                                    :op2 "States"))
                        :ARG2 (p2 / president
                              :mod (v / vice))))
            :ARG1 (p3 / pledge-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (k / keep-02
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (s2 / support-01
                              :ARG0 p
                              :ARG1 (e / effort-01
                                    :ARG0 (c2 / country
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Afghanistan"))
                                    :ARG1 (a / and
                                          :op1 (b / build-01
                                                :ARG0 c2
                                                :ARG1 (f / force
                                                      :mod (s3 / security)
                                                      :poss c2))
                                          :op2 (d / defeat-01
                                                :ARG0 c2
                                                :ARG1 (ii / insurgent
                                                      :mod (c3 / criminal-organization
                                                            :name (n4 / name
                                                                  :op1 "Taliban"))))))))
                  :time (d2 / date-entity
                        :weekday (t / tuesday))
                  :time (t2 / talk-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG2 (p4 / person
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Hamid"
                                    :op2 "Karzai")
                              :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 c2
                                    :ARG2 (p5 / president)))))))
